"target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗倡议中东建立无美以联盟，出于哪些考量？当前中东局势下能建立起来吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 3 月 25 日，伊朗武装部队哈塔姆·安比亚中央司令部发言人向伊斯兰国家喊话，倡议在中东地区建立「一个没有美国和以色列参与的安全和军事联盟」。 该发言人表示，中东不需要一个几千公里之外的国家，一个将伊斯兰国家视为「摇钱树」的国家，一个为以色列安全牺牲别国的国家来保障地区安全。他还质问有美军基地的国家：「如果面临以色列侵略，美国人会为你们开一枪吗？」 伊朗倡议中东建立无美以联盟"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ccd880e8e79102417671b19e902a1dd2_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2020252058335274061"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsoConure0LsHEAMaCTExODg5OTAxNSC5yI/OBjAAOLACQAxyEzIwMjAyNTIwNTgzMzUyNzQwNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1774509027.741504", "card_id": "Q_2020398574286947708", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2526 赛季 NBA 常规赛湖人 137:130 步行者，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-62bb4f0b08bd81d25e8f77c63837b74b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2020398574286947708"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIsoConure0LsHEAMaCTExODkwMTc0OCCt2ZHOBjAAOBNADXITMjAyMDM5ODU3NDI4Njk0NzcwOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1774509027.742043", "card_id": "Q_2012198131295545035", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "蔡依林的《布拉格广场》改编版，被调侃「一个是布拉格广场一个是万达广场」，你更喜欢哪个版本？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[视频]"}, "imag